original: Kvillner, Erik Gunnar, komminister, Gemla, f. 23/3/02 i Algutsboda, Kro-nob. 1. G. 33 m. Astrid Andersson. Barn: Gudrun f. 34, Gunnar 41, Bo 44. — Stud:ex. i Lund 26, teol. fil. ex. där 28, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Växjö stift 31. Tjg. som past:adj. i Algutsboda o. Kalvsvik samt som v. kommin. i Föra, kommin. i Öja sed. 34.
translated: Kvillner, Erik Gunnar, curate, Gemla, b. 23/3/02 in Algutsboda, Kronoberg county. Married in 1933 to Astrid Andersson. Children: Gudrun b. 1934, Gunnar b. 1941, Bo b. 1944. Completed high school in Lund in 1926, theological bachelor's degree in 1928, theological candidate, practical theological examination, and ordained as a priest in the Diocese of Växjö in 1931. Served as assistant pastor in Algutsboda and Kalvsvik, and as assistant curate in Föra, and curate in Öja since 1934.
